m/2024/9/9/24236804/airpods-max-second-gen-price-specs-features-release-date</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T13:30:36-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T13:30:36-04:00</updated><title> Apple Watch 即将推出睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;事件幻灯片，显示 Apple 通过 Apple Watch 检测到“可能存在睡眠呼吸暂停”的警告通知。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XKvdVTCaD0_Gnakb5YWAzJd8x3o=/0x51:997x716/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574344/lcimg_bf067d6e_79ae_4512_94 ec_4cd461543748.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;b0cez5&quot;>;Apple 正在为 Apple Watch 添加睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能。 Apple Watch Series 9 即将推出新功能，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features- release-date&quot;>;刚刚发布的 Series 10&lt;/a>;，以及 Apple 在周一的产品活动中宣布的 Apple Watch Ultra 2。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;xsqTsd&quot;>;睡眠呼吸暂停是&lt;a href= “https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/sleep-apnea/symptoms-causes/syc-20377631&quot;>;一种导致您在睡眠时停止呼吸的疾病&lt;/a>;。睡眠呼吸暂停是可穿戴设备制造商已经研究了一段时间的一项功能，三星已获得 FDA 批准，可以通过 Galaxy Watch 进行睡眠呼吸暂停跟踪 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/ 9/24067819/samsung-galaxy-watch-sleep-apnea-tracker-fda-de-novo-authorization&quot;>;今年早些时候&lt;/a>;。苹果表示，它正在使用手表上的加速计来监控一项新指标，该指标被称为“呼吸障碍”。您将能够在“健康”应用中查看夜间呼吸障碍值。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Apple&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot; gkDI9V&quot;>;该公司预计...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep-apnea-detection -feature-series-9-10-ultra-2&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep-apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep-apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry></feed>